ygData.messageBody:
I just hit 37 in OT. I find my best xp is in pickup groups. I never
really was good at solo. I did fear kite in LOIO, decent xp, but
charm kite and denons kite can't seem to get the knack. Any
suggestions? I heard that you can kite 2 or 3 thing with brass and
sow, but always wound up beaten and fearing it to keep from dying.
Maybe the new tables will allow me to hit harder. My best so far is
36 with 11/29 icetooth.
